0</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a8e180055595c5187a8f936b49b89d49dd4c720f","tid":1534211,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"最好比雜種雞姦屌死埋"},{"pid":"5a2d4c899118e9c0e9a7148a14537346926b4006","tid":1534211,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"3月新聞喎清 <br />\n走左啦話?"},{"pid":"cec6f56d9802b1ff3c212272f038c39ffcba2373","tid":1534211,"uid":196697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2d4c899118e9c0e9a7148a14537346926b4006","tid":1534211,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"3月新聞喎清 <br />\n走左啦話?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"之前有新聞話九月去希臘讀書，但你估走唔走到？"},{"pid":"f2b6fe1e050421ff00fbdbc18ce0063421baf4e0","tid":1534211,"uid":81919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"d7d0936258a5e86554b6afb10212c199e708599b","tid":1534211,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"香港呢個孤兒仔<br />\n流落到谷底<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1EMLpV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1EMLpV.png&h=a8c2239a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid